# Captured device/CLI output from QA runs — never commit.
# These are raw logcat and expo-start dumps. They carry real auth user UUIDs (user
# PII) and trip gitleaks' generic-api-key entropy heuristic, which reddened
# secret-scan on every PR in 2026-07 (see .gitleaksignore, entries dated 2026-07-19).
docs/qa/evidence/
*_logcat.txt
expo-start*.out.txt

# Local signing/credential helper scripts — never commit
set-signing-creds.ps1
*-signing-creds.ps1

# Stray local documents and store assets at the repo root
/*.pdf
/ap store/
